node.text: Beautiful afternoon in Ohio, Camp anywhere you can park? Pick me! @ikamper @jeep #getoutside #overlanding #offroad #staydirty #jeeplife #gladiator #davecanterbury

node.text: Most of our courses for the remainder of 2021 are now full. We will be releasing the 2022 schedule in about October. We will be @smokymountainknifeworks in October for Dealer weekend doing some talks and demos if you don’t get a chance to get to the school this year, come see us for that event. #training #survival #bushcraft #offroad #overlanding #camping #hiking #communicationskills #selfreliance #staydirty #davecanterbury

node.text: Running some trials on the portable HF rig today! #communication #selfreliance #preparedness #naturaldisaster #getoutside #staydirty #alwaysastudent #davecanterbury

node.text: Checking fit up and compatibility of a couple prototypes we have in the pipeline. Most projects take about a year of R&D if it requires tooling purchases etc… but gear design and bringing products to market is all a continuous mindset for any business that manufactures product. #outdoorgear #entrepreneur #smallbusiness #familybusiness #design #development #getoutside #staydirty #thinkahead #davecanterbury

node.text: @brooksanddunn and @realtravistritt tonight with my girl! Love me some good country music and waited 30 years to see Travis live! Thank you @iriscanterbury #countrymusic #livelife #blessed #soulmate #concert #musiclover

node.text: This is a shot of a recent raised bed made for video by @corporalscorner, if you are not subscribed to his YT channel you are missing some great content using simple tools to do some nice builds. Being the lead Instructor at #thepathfinderschoolllc he uses our teaching mentality in every video and they are packed with small tidbits of excellent information #bushcraft #toolheavy #the5cs #bushcraft101 #getoutside #staydirty #davecanterbury

node.text: A chuckbox can take on many forms, this small kit covers everything I need for camp cooking on the road. We are currently developing an inclusive kit for one of my favorite Sponsor companies, I can’t wait to show you the results! #offroad #campcooking #getoutside #overlanding #jeeplife #davecanterbury

node.text: The removable trays in the front of the @deckedusa system allow storage of small and quick access items to make truck organizations much less of a chore, with everything contained and easy to get at when needed it has become one of the favorite pieces of my Gladiator build! #jeeplife #offroad #getoutside #davecanterbury

node.text: A few projects from one student over the weekend in the BC 101. Notice the Spoon made specifically for also reaching the near 90 degree angle of a Bush-pot when serving food.
